  "response": "Here are some highly-rated solar panel installation providers near Mission Viejo, California:\n\n1. **Sunrun**  \n   - A national leader in residential solar with strong customer reviews.  \n   - Offers solar panel installation, leasing, and financing options.  \n   - Website: [sunrun.com](https://www.sunrun.com)  \n\n2. **SunPower by Stellar Solar**  \n   - A local provider with a strong reputation for high-efficiency solar panels and quality service.  \n   - Located in nearby San Marcos, CA.  \n   - Website: [sunsol.com](https://www.sunsol.com)  \n\n3. **Baker Electric Home Energy**  \n   - Based in Escondido, CA, Baker Electric is known for excellent customer service and expertise in solar installation.  \n   - Offers solar, battery storage, and energy efficiency solutions.  \n   - Website: [bakerelectric.com](https://www.bakerelectric.com)  \n\n4. **Semper Solaris**  \n   - A veteran-owned company with a strong presence in Southern California.  \n   - Known for excellent customer service and competitive pricing.  \n   - Website: [sempersolaris.com](https://www.sempersolaris.com)  \n\n5. **SolarMax**  \n   - A solar provider with over 30 years of experience, offering customized solutions for homeowners in Mission Viejo.  \n   - Website: [solarmax.com](https://www.solarmax.com)  \n\nBefore choosing a provider, consider obtaining multiple quotes, checking reviews on platforms like Yelp or Google, and verifying their licensing and certifications. Mission Viejo is in Orange County, so ensure the company operates in your area.",
